						               													<description>&amp;ldquo;Behold, I, even I, will bring a sword upon you, and I will destroy your high places. Your altars shall become desolate, and your incense altars shall be broken, and I will cast down your slain before your idols&amp;hellip;&amp;rdquo;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Save a dying land before darkness comes in this kingdom-defense board game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Fall of Oakhaven is a fully cooperative, strategy-adventure game for 1 to 4 players. Players will choose one of four Heroes to hide and preserve the Scrolls in a pick-up-and-deliver fashion. However, the land is being filled with horrible creatures during each round, which will eventually make saving the kingdom much harder. Do you fight the creatures or race to hide the Scrolls before time runs out? Defeating the threats gives you experience points in the form of Blessing, Wisdom, Power and Gold tokens. These tokens strengthen your Skills and Armory cards. Playing your hand of Armory Cards and Skills will require strategy once you enter the 6 Stronghold locations, where boss fights will test your endurance. Will you have enough time?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the spirit of Defenders of the Realm and Legends of Andor, The Fall of Oakhaven pits Heroes against time and creatures of darkness, in an attempt to preserve the kingdom from complete and utter doom.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
